498
00:28:40,593 --> 00:28:41,511
Até mais tarde.

499
00:28:42,095 --> 00:28:42,929
Até.

500
00:29:08,538 --> 00:29:10,290
Escute, falei com seus pais.

501
00:29:11,166 --> 00:29:12,709
